chat.msg: hola, q tal? ready to start?
Ready!
great! okay, currently i see a twig to my left leading to an island with a tiger
where should i go?
Turn to your left and use the twig to cross over to the island with the tiger
cool! now i can see the tiger on the island
what's next?
cross over to the island with the tiger
oops, seems like we’re already on the island with the tiger
which way next, mate?
look to your right and there should be a twig
don't see a twig here, but there're two islands
one with parrot to my southwest and the other with a butterfly to southeast. where to now, buddy?
walk toward the parrot island
alrighty, now i'm with our feathery friend, the parrot! and hey, i can see an elephant to my left! what's the next move, pal?
walk toward the elephants and rocks
okay, now i'm next to the elephant and the 3 rocks are visible to southeast
where to now?
use the rocks to cross over to the island with the giraffe
seems like there's no path to giraffe from here mate
but i can see a frog looking at me from a different island. should i go to the frog?
yes go to the frog
just hopped over to the frog
left to me is a crocodile giving a mean look. and i see the same big elephant to the crocodile's left
go back to the island with the elephant
Aye Aye! I'm back on the elephant's island
what is around you that will allow you to cross over to another island?
looking around, i see the same crocodile and the familiar parrot
plus, there’s a fairly tall giraffe to my west. what's the plan, bud?
go the giraffe island
roger that, now standing tall with the giraffe! i see a snake to my southeast and two steps east from the snake, i see our treasure! where should i snake off to now, mate?
cross over to the snake island
made it safely to the snake island! i can actually see our treasure from here! just two steps away! shall we go grab it?
go grab the treasure!
aarr matey, treasure is ours now! we did it, friend, yay! *finished*

ready!
cool! so, you're near the white dog, right? walk a few steps to your left towards a wooden bench, but don't go too far

head back where the white dog is

great! now, cross the trail again and continue south, going down the map
you should see another white dog. head there
do I need to cross any logs to get to the white dog?
nope, just stay on your path
the other white dog is just sitting next to a picnic. can you see it?
I am by the dog and picnic
well done! now go west, you'll see a mat with a bowl of berries on it
go over it, still heading west
im at the bowl of berries, where next
awesome, keep on track buddy! now, there's a branch crossing the river to the north
cross it
is the branch by yellow fish?
yes, that's the one! now, once you've crossed the river, watch out for a green bush
but don't touch it
is the green bush next to the white dog?
no, keep moving past the bush on its right side until you see the florist stand again
okay I see the florist stand
awesome! time to make a left turn now but go below the florist stand
you're doing great!

cool! keep heading west until you come across a big bridge with two people on bikes

well done! pass the bridge till you see two folks reading newspapers on a bench

awesome! now, head a few steps south between the old people and a wooden branch till you reach a green bush

you're doing awesome, my friend! now, head east between the branch and the bush
just a bit more!

great job! now, keep heading east a few more steps
you're very close!

chat.msg: hola, you ready?
ready!
awesome! i'm in the tent up north
where should i head first?
head south until you reach the dog
gotcha, i'm with the dog now, what next buddy?
walk down to the dirt path and follow the dirt path until you see the campfire
okay, at the fire now, it's warm here, where to from here?
head north, walking around the campfire until you run into the mushrooms
okay, standing with the big red mushroom, where now?
walk a little south until you see the path, follow the path to your right until you see the car
alright, i see a blue car, where to now?
make a u turn and head west until you see a fork in the road
okay, i'm here at the fork
which way now?
head south down the path until you see a telescope on your left and bushes on your right
okay, i see the telescope
any specific direction i should head in now?
walk around the telescope, using the path and go in-between the telescope and bush
cool, gotcha, i'm walking past the telescope now, what should i do next?
do you see the bush to your right?
yeah, i see it, should i follow the path to the right of the bush?
no, walk in-between the telescope and bush and head south to the dirt path
okay, i'm on the dirt path now, which way to go?
walk west down the dirt path until you see grey rocks
got it, i'm at the rocks, where to now?
to your right you should see grass and a cabin
yes! i see the house, is this it?
that's it!
woohoo! we made it! *finished* thanks for the directions, couldn't have done it without you
